You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 this weekend to take a test drive of this great vehicle!

Description: Land a bargain on this 2016 Ford F-150 before someone else takes it home. Comfortable but easy to maneuver, its dependable Automatic transmission and its strong Twin Turbo Regular Unleaded V-6 3.5 L/213 engine have lots of pep for a discount price. It's loaded with the following options: Tire Specific Low Tire Pressure Warning, Tailgate Rear Cargo Access, Steel Spare Wheel, Side Impact Beams, Securilock Anti-Theft Ignition (pats) Engine Immobilizer, Safety Canopy System Curtain 1st And 2nd Row Airbags, Regular Box Style, Rear Cupholder, Rear Child Safety Locks, and Pickup Cargo Box Lights. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 this weekend to get a deal that no one can beat!

Description: Grab a score on this 2015 Kia Optima LX before someone else snatches it. Spacious yet easy to maneuver, its tried-and-true Automatic transmission and its trusty Regular Unleaded I-4 2.4 L/144 engine have lots of charm for an inexpensive price. It's loaded with the following options: Window Grid Antenna, Wheels: 16 Alloy, Variable Intermittent Wipers, Urethane Gear Shift Knob, Trunk Rear Cargo Access, Trip Computer, Transmission: 6-Speed Automatic w/Sportmatic, Transmission w/Driver Selectable Mode, Tires: P205/65R16, and Tire Specific Low Tire Pressure Warning. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 this weekend to take a test drive of this great vehicle!

Description: Land a score on this 2013 Toyota 4Runner before it's too late. Comfortable but easy to maneuver, its dependable Automatic transmission and its strong Gas V6 4.0L/241 engine have lots of charm for a bargain price. It is well equipped with the following options: Windshield de-icer, Vehicle stability control (VSC), Variable intermittent windshield wipers w/mist cycle, Variable gear pwr rack & pinion steering, Traction control (TRAC), Tire Pressure Monitor System, Smart Stop Technology (SST), Skid plates -inc: engine, fuel tank, Side-impact door beams, and Rear window defogger w/timer. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 this weekend to take a test drive of this great vehicle!

You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 today to take a test drive of this great vehicle!

Whether you want to be entertained or informed, to laugh, think, or sing, XM has the perfect channel for you - coast-to-coast, and in digital-quality sound. 3 trial months - no obligation (Available in the 48 contiguous United States. For more information, visit gm.xmradio.com. Description: Land a steal on this 2003 GMC Yukon XL while we have it. Spacious but easy-moving, its worry-free Automatic transmission and its strong Gas V8 5.3L/325 engine have lots of charm for a low price. It is stocked with these options: Wipers, intermittent, front wet-arm w/pulse washers, Windows, power-inc: driver express-down & lockout features, Wheels, 4 - 16 x 7 (40.6 cm x 17.8 cm) 6-lug bright machined aluminum-inc: steel spare, Warning tones, headlamp on, key-in-ignition, driver safety belt unfasten, turn signal on, Visors, padded, Shale-colored, driver & passenger side w/cloth trim, extenders, illuminated vanity mirrors & corner storage pockets on back of visors, Trailering wiring harness, 7-wire, Traction assist system, electronic, Tow/haul mode selector, button located at end of shift lever, Suspension, rear, multi-link w/coil springs, and Suspension, front, independent torsion bar, & stabilizer bar. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 this weekend to take a test drive of this great vehicle!

Description: Snag a steal on this 2014 Ford Taurus SE before it's too late. Comfortable yet easy to maneuver, its worry-free Automatic transmission and its durable Regular Unleaded V-6 3.5 L/213 engine have lots of soul for a budget-friendly price. It's loaded with the following options: Window Grid Antenna, Wheels: 17 Painted Aluminum, Urethane Gear Shift Knob, Trunk Rear Cargo Access, Trip Computer, Transmission: 6-Speed SelectShift Automatic -inc: sport mode and shifter button activation, Tires: P235/60R17 A/S BSW, Systems Monitor, Strut Front Suspension w/Coil Springs, and Speed Sensitive Variable Intermittent Wipers. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 today to take a test drive of this great vehicle!

Description: Win a deal on this 2012 Nissan Versa before someone else takes it home. Spacious yet agile, its low maintenance transmission and its trusty Gas I4 1.8L/110 engine have lots of charm for an inexpensive price. It's loaded with the following options: Zone body construction -inc: front/rear crumple zones, hood deformation point, Vehicle dynamic control (VDC), Variable intermittent windshield wipers w/mist function, Traction control system (TCS), Torsion beam rear suspension w/stabilizer bar, Tire pressure monitoring system (TPMS), Tilt steering column, Steel side-door impact beams, Speed sensitive pwr door locks, and Silver finish interior door handles. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 soon to get a deal that no one can beat!

Description: Grab a deal on this 1999 Ford F-150 before someone else snatches it. Spacious but agile, its dependable transmission and its durable Gas V8 5.4L/330 engine have lots of charm for a discount price. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 this weekend to take a test drive of this great vehicle!

Description: Land a bargain on this 2011 Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD LTZ before it's too late. Comfortable but agile, its tried-and-true Automatic transmission and its strong engine have lots of charm for a low price. It comes equipped with these options: XM Radio is standard on nearly all 2011 GM models and includes 3 months of trial service. Get over 170 channels, including: commercial-free music, sports, news, talk, entertainment, comedy, family and kids' channels, and much more. With XM's incredible range of programming, everything worth listening to is on XM (Not available with (UUL) AM/FM stereo with MP3 compatible CD player and navigation, (UUK) AM/FM stereo with MP3 compatible CD/DVD player and navigation or (UE0) OnStar, delete. Requires a subscription sold separately by XM after the first 90 days. Available only in the 48 contiguous United States and District of Columbia. Visit gm.xmradio.com for details.), Wipers, front intermittent wet-arm with pulse washers, Windows, power with driver Express-Down (Includes front passenger Express-down.), Wheels, 18 (45.7 cm) forged polished aluminum (Includes 18 x 8 (45.7 cm x 20.3 cm) steel spare wheel. Spare not included with (ZW9) pickup box delete unless a spare tire is ordered. Upgradeable to (PYS) 20 (50.8 cm) forged polished aluminum wheels.), Warning tones headlamp on, key-in-ignition, driver and passenger buckle up reminder and turn signal on, Visors, driver and front passenger, sliding with clip and illuminated vanity mirror on driver and passenger-side, Opal Gray-colored, Transmission, 6-speed automatic, heavy-duty, electronically controlled with overdrive and tow/haul mode (Requires (L96) Vortec 6.0L V8 SFI engine.), Transfer case, electronic shift with rotary dial controls (Requires 4WD models), Trailering equipment, heavy-duty includes trailering hitch platform and 2.5- inch receiver with 2 adapter, 7-wire harness (harness includes wires for: park lamps, backup lamps, right turn, left turn, electric brake lead, battery and ground) with independent fused trailering circuits mated to a 7-way sealed connector, wiring harness for after-market trailer brake controller (located in the instrument panel harness) and (JL1) integrated trailer brake controller (Will be deleted if (ZW9) pickup box delete is ordered.), and Trailer brake controller, integrated. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 soon to take a test drive of this great vehicle!

Description: Grab a deal on this 2016 Ford Taurus SHO before it's too late. Spacious but agile, its low maintenance Automatic transmission and its trusty Twin Turbo Premium Unleaded V-6 3.5 L/213 engine have lots of pep for a budget-friendly price. It is well equipped with the following options: Window Grid Antenna, Wheels: 20 Machined Aluminum w/Painted Pockets, Valet Function, Trunk Rear Cargo Access, Trip Computer, Tires: P245/45R20 AS BSW, Systems Monitor, SYNC 3 -inc: enhanced voice recognition communications and entertainment system, 8 LCD touch screen in center stack w/swiping and pinch-to-zoom capabilities, AppLink, 911 assist and 2 smart charging USB ports, Strut Front Suspension w/Coil Springs, and Sport Tuned Suspension. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 soon to take a test drive of this great vehicle!

Description: Land a bargain on this 2016 Ford Expedition before someone else snatches it. Spacious yet agile, its low maintenance Automatic transmission and its trusty Twin Turbo Regular Unleaded V-6 3.5 L/213 engine have lots of pep for a low price. It's loaded with the following options: Window Grid Antenna, Trip Computer, Tailgate/Rear Door Lock Included w/Power Door Locks, Systems Monitor, Steel Spare Wheel, Single Stainless Steel Exhaust w/Chrome Tailpipe Finisher, Side Impact Beams, Securilock Anti-Theft Ignition (pats) Engine Immobilizer, Safety Canopy System Curtain 1st, 2nd And 3rd Row Airbags, and Roof Rack. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 this weekend to drive home in your new car!

Description: Win a steal on this 2010 Chevrolet HHR LS while we have it. Spacious yet agile, its dependable Automatic transmission and its durable Gas/Ethanol I4 2.2L/134 engine have lots of pep for an inexpensive price. Description: Land a score on this 2009 Toyota Tacoma while we have it. Spacious but agile, its tried-and-true Manual transmission and its trusty Gas I4 2.7L/164 engine have lots of zip for a value price. It is well equipped with the following options: Vehicle stability control, Variable-assist pwr rack & pinion steering, Traction control w/off switch, Tire Pressure Monitor System, Tilt & telescopic steering wheel, Sun visors w/front passenger vanity mirror, Side-door impact door beams, Rear mudguards, Rear leaf-spring suspension w/staggered outboard-mounted gas shock absorbers, and Pwr windows. You've done your research, so stop by Laurel Ford Lincoln Kia at 2018 Highway 15 N, Laurel, MS 39440 today to drive home in your new car!
